### Banking Transactions API - Python/FastAPI
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Root Endpoint - API Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### ===================
### TRANSACTIONS
### ===================

### Create a deposit transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 1000.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Create another deposit to a different account
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 500.00,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Create a transfer transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 150.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "transfer"
}

### Create a withdrawal transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "withdrawal"
}

### Get all transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions

### Get transactions filtered by account
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345

### Get transactions filtered by type
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?type=transfer

### Get transactions filtered by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?from=2024-01-01&to=2024-12-31

### Combine multiple filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345&type=deposit

### Export transactions as CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/export?format=csv

### ===================
### ACCOUNTS
### ===================

### Get account balance
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-12345/balance

### Get account summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-12345/summary

### Calculate simple interest (5% annual rate for 30 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-12345/interest?rate=0.05&days=30

### ===================
### VALIDATION ERRORS
### ===================

### Invalid account format
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "INVALID-ACC",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Negative amount
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": -50.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Invalid currency
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "INVALID",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Too many decimal places
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 100.123,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Missing required account for transfer
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "transfer"
}

### Same account for transfer
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "transfer"
}
